","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis nation of mine has been granted mercy. Their punishment is not in the Hereafter. Their punishment is in the world through persecution, earthquakes, and slaughter.\" Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4278 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19081,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/10\/deeds-not-accepted-murderer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36334,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Murder: Good deeds not accepted from killers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever kills a believer without a just cause, Allah will not accept any of his obligatory or voluntary good deeds.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4270 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u062a\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6179,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/10\/envy-destroys-good-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":36334,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hasad: Beware of envy that destroys good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of envy, for it devours good deeds just as fire devours wood or grass.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4903 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u062f\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17207,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/17\/trials-affliction-sabr-rank\/","url_meta":{"origin":36334,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Patience: Allah afflicts him to compensate for his deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Jallaj ibn Hakim reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, if a servant is destined for a rank he has not achieved by his good deeds, Allah puts him to trial in his body, or his wealth, or his children. Then, Allah makes him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u064